$t[10] = 'Dhab ahaanbaan u siinay Nabi Daawuud fadli (dheeraad) xaganaga ah, waxaana nidhi buurahoow ka celceliya tasbiixda, shimbirahoowna (la celceliya tasbiixda,) waxaana u jilcincy birta.';
